  "instructions_to_main_agent": "Ensure the overall look matches a high-end wildlife magazine. Use Playfair Display for headers and DM Sans for body. Do not deviate to blue or generic templates. Utilize the defined css variables in tailwind config for custom colors. Implement the floating WhatsApp and top ticker. All images MUST be mapped as defined in this media block."
